msgstr ""

#: ../../../developer_guide/contribution_guide.md:179
msgid ""
"[Code Walk-through](https://github.com/zhaochenyang20/Awesome-ML-SYS-"
"Tutorial/tree/main/sglang/code-walk-through) for a deeper look into SGLang’s "
"workflow."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../developer_guide/contribution_guide.md:180
msgid ""
"[GTC-2026 Training Lab](https://drive.google.com/file/"
"d/1mwOZEtipNLJzrflCTodj34KhuOZEoEw5/view?usp=drive_link) for hands-on "
"practices of how to do optimization, benchmarking, or profiling on a "
"launched SGLang instance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../developer_guide/contribution_guide.md:182
msgid ""
"If you have any questions or want to start a discussion, please feel free to "
"ask in our [Slack channel](https://slack.sglang.io)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../developer_guide/contribution_guide.md:184
msgid "Thank you for your interest in SGLang. Happy coding!"
msgstr ""
